text: Schönemann, also spelled Schoenemann, is a German surname. "Schaneman", is the modern spelling. See: * Dora Schönemann (born 1911), German swimmer * Hinnerk Schönemann (born 1974), German actor * Lili Schönemann (1758–1817), daughter of a banker from Frankfurt * Peter Schönemann, German psychometrician and statistician * Theodor Schönemann (1812–1868), German mathematician
